item.title: [HIVE-23315] Remove empty line from the end of SHOW EXTENDED TABLES and SHOW MATERIALIZED VIEWS
item.description:
At the end of each SHOW EXTENDED TABLES; and SHOW MATERIALIZED VIEWS; command there is an empty line like this:

+------------+----------------+
|  tab_name  |   table_type   |
+------------+----------------+
| sample_07  | MANAGED_TABLE  |
| sample_08  | MANAGED_TABLE  |
| web_logs   | MANAGED_TABLE  |
|            | NULL           |
+------------+----------------+

It should be removed.
item.summary: Remove empty line from the end of SHOW EXTENDED TABLES and SHOW MATERIALIZED VIEWS
